name: Fishwar
description: FishWar – The Future of AI-Powered GameFi on SEI FishWar pioneers the future of AI GameFi in a post-apocalyptic ocean realm. Players dive into strategic combat, epic quests, and resource challenges, earning rewards through a dynamic, AI-driven experience. Our cutting-edge AI crafts a living battlefield that adapts to every move, while diverse earning mechanics—from combat victories to resource mastery—empower players to thrive.
